Kami benar-benar kelelahan setiap hari.

60
00:06:47,020 --> 00:06:48,590
Maafkan aku.

61
00:06:48,590 --> 00:06:51,450
Aku akan mentraktir kalian makan.

62
00:06:51,450 --> 00:06:53,830
