80
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:41,040
Maaf aku terlambat. Maafkan aku.

81
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,810
Apa yang kau lakukan?

82
00:07:42,810 --> 00:07:45,310
Kau hanya telat 30 menit.

83
00:07:45,310 --> 00:07:46,470
Apa?

84
