586
00:44:43,920 --> 00:44:45,390
Ayo minum!

587
00:44:46,250 --> 00:44:47,910
Apa yang paling penting dalam hidup?

588
00:44:47,910 --> 00:44:51,410
Kita bekerja sampai lelah, minum bir,
